Pisa is an application for the AVRmega328P microcontroller.

Its principle reason for being is to control an AD7124 24-bit ADC.

To build and install the application :-

  $ make
  $ cd ../bali
  $ avril pisa

To build and install the application and bootloader :-

  connect the ICSP cable between bali and pisa

  $ make image
  $ cd ../bali
  $ (. ./defs.sh && cd ../pisa && make avp)

